Hollywood start Sylvester Stallone attends Warner Bros Premiere Of "The Suicide Squad" at The Landmark Westwood on August 02 - 2021 wearing one of his Nautilus hit, the great 5980/1AR in stainless steel and rose gold.

node.text:
Mind blowing timepieces🤩
The @JacobAndCo Bugatti Chiron Tourbillon in the 4 most spectacular and evocative variants💣 Which one is your favorite?

The case is inspired by the flowing lines of the Chiron and the movement, or “engine block,” intended to duplicate the Bugatti engine, is placed under a massive sapphire crystal, on display for all to see. With the push of right-hand crown of the timepiece the engine comes to life, just like a true internal combustion engine. 
The movement is set with a total of 578 exquisite components. 
Right now Jacob’s workshop is doing something no one has ever even attempted before: to seamlessly combine engines and watches💯

node.text:
The only way to get a Daytona at list price and without a waiting list is to win the 24 Hours of LeMans😁
Kamui Kobayashi, Mike Conway and José Maria Lopez have won the 24 Hours of Le Mans 2021, the 89th edition of the legendary endurance race.  Double for Toyota in the Hypercar class with Alpine completing the podium.  Double also for Ferrari in GT class.
All the winning pilots were awarded with the iconic cup and with a rolex daytona cosmograph black dial
•
📸 Rolex | @orologiepassioni (Marco Bi)

node.text:
Pop icon also know The "King of Pop" Michael Jackson, leading figure of 20th century musical culture, who passed prematurely in summer 2009, wore one of the first and historic @jacobandco ever produced, a stainless steel big size 47mm Five Time Zone with a factory diamond bezel, black leather strap with red accents and a quartz movement.
As part of iconic and heritage timepieces, the Five Time Zone Collection represents the groundbreaking pieces that sparked a revolution in Jacob watch design. They inspired countless competitors but remain unsurpassed. Today, they are the benchmark driving force behind their newest creations.
•
📸 @gettyimages
